 body has no use or meaning after death. 
However, your friend is not entir=
ely correct. If one has a deep attachment 
to the body, mind may be attache=
d to the body even after death, even after 
the connection of the karmendri=
yas and jnanendriyas of the mind to the 
physical body is cut off. Then wha=
t happens to the body does affect the mind 
and its further
 progress.

